@startuml
!theme plain
title YAS — CI/CD Pipeline

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ArrowColor #333333
skinparam FontName Arial
skinparam fontSize 11

start

:**Triggers:**
- PR (open/sync/reopen) → main, dev
- Push → main;

:**Path-filter**
Xác định service thay đổi;

fork
  :**Java CI**
  mvn clean verify
  Checkstyle + SonarQube
  JaCoCo ≥ 70%;
fork again
  :**Node CI**
  ESLint
  npm test --coverage
  npm run build;
end fork

if (Push to feature branch?) then (yes)
  :CI passed
  (không push image);
  stop
else (PR or push to main)
  :**Docker Build & Push**
  → ghcr.io/23120091/<service>:<sha>;
endif

if (Push to **main**?) then (yes)
  :**ArgoCD** detects drift;

  if (Env?) then (dev)
    :Auto-sync (Image Updater);
  elseif (staging)
    :Auto-sync (git tag);
  else (production)
    :Manual sync;
  endif

  :Sync waves → Reloader;

  :Deploy complete;
else (PR)
  :Image ready
  (PR checks passed);
endif

stop

@enduml
